legacy.full_text:
$CHZ - at November’s end if BTC behaves and no nasty macro surprises, I could see this pumping to 40-50 cents by end of the month

It’s down 74% from all time high, strongest narrative for all of November looks like it will be the World Cup.

I said in quoted tweet barring no nasty macro surprises that $CHZ would hit 40-50 cents end of month

It pumped 40% from entry to 29.5 cents, then sadly nuked hard on FTX collapse. 

With CPI coming in at 7.7% and SPX almost 4000, if not for FTX, I do think target would’ve hit.
